        %h2 UNF Spinnaker
        %h5 Official Student Media Source for the University of North Florida
        %p I was given the opportunity to redesign the newspaperâ€™s website, twice. In this most recent version the goals were to better incorporate social media integration, restructure the website to better include the newly renamed Spinnaker Radio and Spinnaker Television, and create a multimedia environment which would allow new student-staff to properly maintain and update it in the upcoming semesters.
