        %h3 Homepage
        %p Above the fold, in addition to a large callout of popular stories, both TV and Radio take up real estate. By including them on the main page, it helps push the multimedia aspect and better demonstrates the products and services which the Spinnaker offers. One challenge when working on this site was including both a leaderboard ad and wide-rectangle above the fold. Revenue from the Ads help ensure the organization continues to operate.
        %p Below the fold are callouts to each of the content departments where the Editor is able to choose which story is featured.
    %article.image
      .item-image
        = image_tag('work/spinnaker-radio.jpg', {:alt => 'Radio Department Screen'})
